name: Germination LIVE VR Art
description:
'Bob VRoss Live Vr Art Stream March 23.
Process of germination, along with some ancient Norse art patterns. This work is dedicated to my dear Mother, who is a lovely botanist.
When I was in middle school, my mother helped me with a science fair project on germination. I was facinated to know about how a seed needs to completely break itself in order to grow.
You are never a "broken" person.
You are a natural being that is in a state of growth. Times are tough, but you are tougher.
